data.description:
No HOA! Discover the perfect blend of tranquility and sophistication in this stunning residence nestled in the heart of Southaven. Recently updated, the home proudly displays a new roof, brand new windows, and modern appliances to enhance your living experience. As you step through the front door, the stained wood flooring greets you, gracing the entry and seamlessly connecting to the dining and living rooms. The living area boasts a natural gas fireplace, setting the perfect ambiance for cozy family evenings.
In the heart of the home, the kitchen stands as a testament to modern luxury with its exquisite quartz countertops, combining both beauty and functionality. Designed for family living, the downstairs space houses four spacious bedrooms accompanied by two full, tastefully designed bathrooms. Venture upstairs to find a personal haven - a dedicated media room for movie enthusiasts with a ceiling mounted projector and a vibrant playroom area for the younger members of the family. This level is also complemented by an additional full bathroom, ensuring convenience at every turn.
The exterior of the home doesn't disappoint either. A highlight of the outdoor space is the sizable 28' x 14' workshop, fully equipped with electricity, ready to serve as a hub for storage, hobbies, or perhaps a personal gym. Privacy and convenience are paramount, evidenced by the wide electric gate leading to the backyard parking area. As an added benefit, the current refrigerator will remain with the home, enhancing the ready-to-move-in appeal.
Located just minutes from local shopping and the Silo Square/Amphitheater entertainment district, this home is a beautiful blend of luxury and comfort, ensuring the best of both worlds - a peaceful sanctuary and seamless connectivity. Don't miss the opportunity to own this piece of paradise in Southaven. Reserve your private viewing quickly.
